steps.instruction:
### Prep
- Finely chop the cilantro
- Drain the tomatoes 

### Steps
1. Place cheese spread in medium bowl; divide into small pieces to soften
2. Shred chicken breast meat (2 cups)
3. Chop cilantro
4. Add all ingredients (except tortillas) to cheese spread; mix with electric mixer until blended
5. Spread mixture evenly over each tortilla and roll up tightly
6. Place on baking sheet (seam-side down); chill 15 minutes or until chilled
7. Cut each tortilla roll into 10 (1-inch) pieces. Serve.

food.name: Canned Diced Tomatoes with Green Chilies
